Package: ecoreview
Title: Interactive Review Interface for Ecological Data Extraction
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Nathan", "Layman", , "nathan.layman@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: Provides an interactive Shiny interface for human validation of
    ecological interaction data extracted from scientific literature. Works with
    databases created by the ecoextract package, allowing researchers to review
    OCR text alongside extracted records, edit fields, track changes with full
    audit trails, and calculate extraction accuracy metrics.
